FuncDef: The display aaa statistics access-type-authenreq command displays the number of NAC authentication requests. The display aaa statistics access-type-authenreq command displays the number of NAC authentication requests. This command is supported only on the CE6863H, CE6863H-K, CE6881H, CE6881H-K, CE6820H, CE6820H-K and CE6820S.
